I"ª<p>After API Days London, and Nordic APIs Summit in Stockholm, Scottie beamed me to API Strat Boston 2016 for the final part of my OpenAPI specification (fka. Swagger specification) talk series: <em>OpenAPI Trek Beyond API Documentation</em>. This last talk is the (not so uncommon) story of how I came to use Swagger/OpenAPI for API documentation and how it changed many things beyond API documentation.</p>

